<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN228-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai, atu. tuṟai, āṇantappaiyuḷ. avaṉai aiyūrmuṭavaṉār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN228">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kalañcey kōvē kalañcey kōvē</l>
<l>yiruṭiṇin taṉṉa kurūuttiraṭ parūuppukai</l>
<l>yakaliru vicumpi ṉūṉṟuñ cūḷai</l>
<l>naṉantalai mūtūrk kalañcey kōvē</l>
<l>yaḷiyai nīyē yāṅkā kuvaiko</l>
<l>ṉilamvarai cūṭṭiya nīṇeṭun tāṉaip</l>
<l>pulavar pukaḻnta poyyā nallicai</l>
<l>virikatir ñāyiṟu vicumpivarn taṉṉa</l>
<l>cēṇviḷaṅku ciṟappiṟ cempiyar marukaṉ</l>
<l>koṭinuṭaṅ kiyāṉai neṭumā vaḷavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟēva rulaka meytiṉa ṉātali</l>
<l>ṉaṉṉōṟ kavikkuṅ kaṇṇakaṉ ṟāḻi</l>
<l>vaṉaital vēṭṭaṉai yāyi ṉeṉaiyatūu</l>
<l>mirunilan tikiriyāp perumalai</l>
<l>maṇṇā vaṉaita lollumō niṉakkē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">O vessel-making king! O vessel-making king! </l>
<l corresp="4ab">In the old town of vast area </l>
<l corresp="3">with a kiln that supports, in the wide dark sky, </l>
<l corresp="2">a big [colon of] smoke, brilliance accumulated like darkness become firm, </l>
<l corresp="4cd">O vessel-making king! </l>
<l corresp="5">Pitiable are you. What will become of you? </l>
<l corresp="10">Vaḷavan on a tall horse, with banners swaying on [his] elephants, </l>
<l corresp="9">descendant of the Cempiyar of far-shining excellence </l>
<l corresp="8">that is like the wide-rayed sun climbing the sky, </l>
<l corresp="7">of unlying fame that is praised by poets, </l>
<l corresp="6">with a lengthy long army which was laid out up to the limits of the ground, </l>
<l corresp="11">because he [now] has reached the world of the gods, </l>
<l corresp="13a-c">if you need to form </l>
<l corresp="12">an urn wide [enough] in area to cover such a one, </l>
<l>is it at all possible for you to form from clay (13d+15)</l>
<l corresp="14">the big mountain with the large earth as the wheel? </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
